   "source": [
    "# YOLO-Bad-Triangle — Adversarial Sweep\n",
    "\n",
    "Runs the full BUILD → ATTACK → DEFEND sweep on a GPU.\n",
    "\n",
    "**Before running:** Make sure the runtime is set to GPU.\n",
    "`Runtime → Change runtime type → T4 GPU`"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
